atomicMintAddLiquidity(bool,address,addr.details: The caller of this method needs to approve `amountCollateral` collateral to be spent by this contract.

params.amountCollateral: Amount of collateral to deposit and mint long and short tokens against.
params.callingAsEOA: If True, caller has balance of collateral and expects to receive back all LP  tokens + dust.
params.deadline: Unix timestamp that will force the transaction to revert if minded after this time.
params.longShortPair: LSP contract address to mint position on.
params.minLpTokens: Minimum number of LP tokens to mint
params.router: Contract to call to exchange long and short tokens.

atomicMintSellOneSide(bool,bool,address,.details: The caller of this method needs to approve `amountCollateral` collateral to be spent by this contract.

params.amountCollateral: Amount of collateral to deposit and mint long and short tokens against.
params.callingAsEOA: If True, caller has balance of collateral and expects to receive back all long/short tokens.
params.deadline: `Router.swapExactTokensForTokens` param: time before transaction must be mined.
params.longShortPair: LSP contract address to mint position on.
params.router: Contract to call to exchange long and short tokens.
params.sellLong: If True, converts all long tokens into short, else the opposite.
params.swapPath: `Router.swapExactTokensForTokens` param: path with which to swap token to sell for the other.

atomicMintAddLiquidity(bool,address,addr.notice: Mint long and short tokens and deposit them all into a UniV2 Pool.

atomicMintSellOneSide(bool,bool,address,.notice: Mint long and short tokens and convert all of one side into the other.
